      <p class='procedural' id='S6CV0386P1-03948'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0386P1_20020611_WH_48' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="italic">Sitting suspended.</span>
